8
00:00:20,030 --> 00:00:23,070
Now, it’s an official holiday in China,

9
00:00:23,070 --> 00:00:26,470
where women get a half day off of work

10
00:00:26,470 --> 00:00:27,530
so they can have afternoon tea

11
00:00:27,530 --> 00:00:30,119
at the Ritz Carlton in Shanghai.

12
00:00:30,119 --> 00:00:32,220
And do lots of online shopping.

13
00:00:32,220 --> 00:00:33,920
Vladimir Lenin would be so proud.

14
00:00:33,920 --> 00:00:35,679
I bet he’s looking down right now

15
