from communist heaven and...

16
00:00:37,190 --> 00:00:38,219
oh, wait.

17
00:00:38,220 --> 00:00:39,540
Never mind.

18
00:00:39,540 --> 00:00:40,100
In the past,

19
00:00:40,100 --> 00:00:42,600
China has celebrated International Women’s
Day

20
00:00:42,609 --> 00:00:44,579
in some unique ways,

21
00:00:44,579 --> 00:00:48,899
