to celebrate International Teenage Boys’
Day.

25
00:00:53,949 --> 00:00:55,609
But that was two years ago.

26
00:00:55,609 --> 00:00:57,719
Today, as the Me Too movement

27
00:00:57,719 --> 00:00:59,269
against sexual harassment

28
00:00:59,269 --> 00:01:01,960
is making waves across the globe,

29
00:01:01,960 --> 00:01:04,329
have things changed for women in China?

30
00:01:04,329 --> 00:01:05,630
For more on this,

31
00:01:05,630 --> 00:01:07,280
