36
00:01:11,670 --> 00:01:12,710
So Shelley,

37
00:01:12,710 --> 00:01:13,740
have you seen improvements

38
00:01:13,740 --> 00:01:15,509
in how women are treated in China

39
00:01:15,509 --> 00:01:17,380
on International Women’s Day?

40
00:01:17,380 --> 00:01:18,770
Oh definitely, Chris.

41
00:01:18,770 --> 00:01:20,789
Just take a look at this page from Tmall,

42
00:01:20,789 --> 00:01:23,189
China’s biggest online shopping site.

43
00:01:23,189 --> 00:01:24,340
In Chinese it says,

44
00:01:24,340 --> 00:01:26,290
March 8, Queen’s Day,

45
00:01:26,290 --> 00:01:28,159
