141
00:04:15,180 --> 00:04:16,720
on International Women’s Day

142
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:19,330
about sexual harassment on public transit.

143
00:04:19,330 --> 00:04:20,860
Wait, they were arrested for

144
00:04:20,860 --> 00:04:22,750
planning to pass out stickers?

145
00:04:22,750 --> 00:04:24,240
Yeah, they didn’t even get to

146
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:26,090
actually pass out the stickers.

147
00:04:26,090 --> 00:04:28,090
They were arrested ahead of time.

148
00:04:28,090 --> 00:04:30,080
And then accused of being foreign spies.

149
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:31,940
You know, the usual.

150
00:04:31,940 --> 00:04:33,350
So what I’m getting from this is that

151
00:04:33,350 --> 00:04:36,050
things are not getting better for women in
China.

152
00:04:36,050 --> 00:04:37,970
Well, ok, to be fair,

153
00:04:37,970 --> 00:04:39,190
