154
00:04:39,190 --> 00:04:40,500
is happening at all

155
00:04:40,500 --> 00:04:42,140
is better than it was.

156
00:04:42,140 --> 00:04:43,920
But as to whether there will be any change

157
00:04:43,920 --> 00:04:46,540
when it comes to sexual harassment in China,

158
00:04:46,540 --> 00:04:48,070
that will take a lot longer.

159
00:04:48,070 --> 00:04:49,630
Take the anti-sexual harassment law

160
00:04:49,630 --> 00:04:52,000
that was passed in 2005.

161
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,000
It just says,

162
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:55,810
"Sexual harassment against women is banned.

163
00:04:55,810 --> 00:04:57,720
The victims shall be entitled to complain

164
00:04:57,720 --> 00:05:00,920
to the entity or the relevant organs."

165
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:01,930
So you can complain,

166
00:05:01,930 --> 00:05:02,930
but the law doesn’t say

167
00:05:02,930 --> 00:05:05,540
what will be done after your complaint.

168
00:05:05,540 --> 00:05:08,190
So the anti-sexual harassment law

169
00:05:08,190 --> 00:05:09,380
is just a suggestion.

170
00:05:09,380 --> 00:05:11,500
Practically speaking, yes.

171
00:05:11,500 --> 00:05:14,010
And is sexual harassment against men banned?

172
00:05:14,010 --> 00:05:15,130
Oh wow.

173
